1981年，夏默创办了周末大学课程，允许在职的成年人参与每月第三个周末密集的课程计划，并许诺他们四年内可以毕业。<ref>{{cite news | title = Weekends Made for College | last = Wood | first = Deborah Leigh | newspaper = Chicago Tribune | date = 1981-11-29 | url = http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/chicagotribune/access/627217852.html?dids=627217852:627217852&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&type=historic&date=Nov+29%2C+1981&author=&pub=Chicago+Tribune&desc=Weekends+made+for+college&pqatl=google | format = fee required | accessdate = 2010-05-05 | archive-date = 2012-10-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121026142250/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/chicagotribune/access/627217852.html?dids=627217852:627217852&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&type=historic&date=Nov+29,+1981&author=&pub=Chicago+Tribune&desc=Weekends+made+for+college&pqatl=google | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Weekend Program | url = http://www.shimer.edu/academicprograms/undergraduate/weekendprogram.cfm | publisher = Shimer College | accessdate = 2011-02-22 | archive-date = 2010-12-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101223000719/http://shimer.edu/academicprograms/undergraduate/weekendprogram.cfm | dead-url = yes }}</ref> 周末大学的学生来自全国各地，有的甚至要往返遥远的佛罗里达和纽约，他们的年龄介乎23岁至70岁。<ref>{{cite web|title=The Shimer Experience: 1995–1997 Catalogue |publisher=Shimer College |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/19970713050110/http://www.shimer.edu/option1.html |archivedate=1997-07-13 |url=http://www.shimer.edu/option1.html |accessdate=2010-04-28 |deadurl=yes }}</ref> 2010年，这类学生有35至40名。
<ref>{{cite news | title = Living for the Weekend College | date = 2010-05-06 | newspaper = Chicago Tribune | url = http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/education/today/chi-edtoday-weekendcollege-050610,0,373920.story | accessdate = 2010-05-06 | archive-date = 2010-08-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100811103516/http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/education/today/chi-edtoday-weekendcollege-050610,0,373920.story | dead-url = no }}</ref>

1961年，夏默首次为学生提供在巴黎为期一年的国外学习计划，1963年起每两年提供在英国[[牛津大学|牛津大学]]的学习计划。<ref name="TIME">{{cite news|title=Colleges: Unknown, Unsung & Unusual|work=Time|date=1963-04-19|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,830138,00.html|accessdate=2010-04-28|archive-date=2010-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101125173342/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,830138,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |title=Shimer-at-Oxford|journal=The Living Church|year=1967|page=6|oclc=17345342| volume=155}}</ref> 夏默允许8至15名学生在教授的带领下，花费一至两个学期研读“牛津-夏默课程”。<ref name = petersons2006>{{cite book | title = Peterson's Four-Year Colleges| url = https://archive.org/details/undergraduategui00pete_0|page =[https://archive.org/details/undergraduategui00pete_0/page/2249 2249] | location = Lawrenceville, NJ | publisher = Thompson/Peterson's | year = 2006 | edition = 37th | isbn = 0768921538  }}</ref> 学生在第三和第四学年的每一个学期，要从核心课程中选取一门课专修，而其余课程则按照牛津大学的学习科目作个人或小组学术辅导，具体科目由学生自主选定。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.shimer.edu/Oxford/OxfordBrochure.pdf | title = Shimer-in-Oxford | publisher = Shimer College | pages = 5–6 | accessdate = 2010-04-28 | format = PDF | archive-date = 2010-11-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101129113009/http://shimer.edu/Oxford/OxfordBrochure.pdf | dead-url = yes }}</ref>  现在“牛津-夏默课程”已与牛津大学课程紧密相连。夏默的国外学习计划创立于1985年，允许学生与来自牛津大学和美国其他学院的学生一起居住。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.shimer.edu/academicprograms/undergraduate/shimerinoxfordprogram.cfm |title=Shimer-in-Oxford Program |publisher=Shimer College |accessdate=2011-02-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120505114025/http://www.shimer.edu/academicprograms/undergraduate/shimerinoxfordprogram.cfm |archivedate=2012-05-05 }}</ref>

夏默为从幼儿园到12年级的教师设计了提供研究生水平的典籍课程教案。学院不为这些研究生提供奖学金，但他们能从这个课程中获得职业发展信用。该课程以为教师提供所需背景知识的方式补充传统教育的不足，从而更加丰富他们的课堂教案。{{sfn|Shimer College Catalog|2009|p=29}} 这项课程与爱德华·唐纳德·海斯卿二世（E.D. Hirsch, Jr.）于1986年创立的“核心知识基础”相伴发展。爱德华是《文化知识：美国人需要知道什么》一书的作者，<ref>{{cite book  | author = E. D. Hirsch Jr. | year = 1987 | title = Cultural Literacy: What Every American Needs to Know | url = https://archive.org/details/culturalliteracychri00hirs | publisher = Houghton Mifflin  | location = Boston  | isbn = 0394758439}}</ref> 这本书旨在提升人们在基础教育阶段的核心共识。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.coreknowledge.org/mimik/mimik_live_data/view.php?id=1833&record_id=4 | title = Learn About Us | publisher = The Core Knowledge Foundation | accessdate = 2010-04-28 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100418112705/http://www.coreknowledge.org/mimik/mimik_live_data/view.php?id=1833&record_id=4 | archivedate = 2010-04-18 }}</ref>

2007年，夏默实施“典籍+法律课程”计划，为学生提供与[[芝加哥肯特法学院|芝加哥肯特法学院]]（Chicago-Kent College of Law）的联动教学，允许学生将第一年法学院的学龄与夏默学龄连续计算，他们获得法学博士学位的总时间是5年而不是7年。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.insidehighered.com/news/2008/08/25/mergers | last = Jaschik | first = Scott | title = Will More Colleges Merge? | publisher = Inside Higher Ed | date = 2008-08-25 | accessdate = 2010-07-07 | archive-date = 2010-04-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100401201811/http://www.insidehighered.com/news/2008/08/25/mergers | dead-url = no }}</ref> 2009年，夏默还与哈罗德华盛顿学院（Harold Washington College (HWC)）实施这种联合办学计划。华盛顿学院是少数几所提供典籍课程的大学之一，夏默允许华盛顿的学生报读一门夏默课程，<ref>{{cite news | title = A Campus Revival for the Great Books | newspaper = The Chronicle of Higher Education | date = 1999-11-19 | last = Carlson | first = Scott | url = http://faculty.ccc.edu/colleges/wright/greatbooks/News/Articls/Higher%20Ed.htm | accessdate = 2010-06-05 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100706041935/http://faculty.ccc.edu/colleges/wright/greatbooks/News/Articls/Higher%20Ed.htm | archivedate = 2010-07-06 }}</ref> 鼓励他们获取夏默的的学士学位。<ref>{{cite web | title = Dual Admissions at HWC | url = http://hwashington.ccc.edu/admissions/dual.aspx | publisher = Harold Washington College | accessdate = 2010-05-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100516204935/http://hwashington.ccc.edu/admissions/dual.aspx | archive-date = 2010-05-16 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

=== 教师 ===

截至2009年，夏默有11名全职教师及2名教师，<ref name = petersonsmidwest/> 期中12人具有博士学位；4人于1978年随学院迁入沃基根。全部教师平均至少有21年的教龄，<ref name=quickfacts>{{cite web | title = Quick Facts | url = http://www.shimer.edu/aboutshimercollege/quickfacts.cfm | publisher = Shimer College | accessdate = 2010-04-21 | archive-date = 2013-01-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130109031248/http://www.shimer.edu/aboutshimercollege/quickfacts.cfm | dead-url = yes }}</ref>师生比例为1:8。<ref name = petersonsmidwest/>夏默教师具备跨学科教育能力，“能教授任何一门核心课程是他们的理念”。<ref name = bigideas/>{{cref |f}}

=== 入学条件 ===

报读夏默的学生要进行学术潜能评估：如果不具备最低[[成绩平均积点|成绩平均积点]]（GPA），则要求合格的考试成绩。夏默确信所招收的学生对学院有益并对知识界有作为。<ref name = completebook>{{cite book | title = Complete Book of Colleges 2005 | url = https://archive.org/details/completebookofco0000unse_g5f6 | page = [https://archive.org/details/completebookofco0000unse_g5f6/page/1335 1335] | publisher = Princeton Review | edition = revised | year = 2004 | location = New York | isbn = 0375764062}}</ref> 报读者需要撰写一份分析性的学术文章，以展示他们的创造性才能；除此之外，面试也是入学的重要条件。<ref name=admission>{{cite web | title = Admission & Finance | publisher = Shimer College | url = http://www.shimer.edu/admissions/ | accessdate = 2010-04-28 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20100527085307/http://www.shimer.edu/admissions/ | archivedate = 2010-05-27 }}</ref> 对于那些在职的、有大学经历的申请者，他们属于典型的非寄宿生，但入学条件也参照寄宿生的标准执行。<ref name = petersons2006/> 报读夏默的申请者成功率为90%，但学院在接受申请之前，会尽量奉劝不符合条件的申请者不要向学院提交申请书。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/chicago-il/shimer-college-1756|title=Shimer College|work=Best Colleges 2010|publisher=US News & World Report|accessdate=2010-04-25|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091231000527/http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/chicago-il/shimer-college-1756|archivedate=2009-12-31}}</ref><ref name="coolcolleges">{{cite book|title=Cool Colleges: For the Hyper-Intelligent, Self-Directed, Late-Blooming and Just Plain Different|last = Asher | first =Donald |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=SRfNZFK5RSMC&pg=PA22|page=22|location = Berkeley, California | publisher = Ten Speed Press | year = 2007 | edition = 2nd | isbn = 1580088392}}</ref>以4分为满分的GPA成绩，夏默要求申请者必须达到3.29分。<ref name = collegedata/> 夏默依照美国广泛采用的标准化大学入学考试要求，在“成绩平均绩点”和“学术评估测试”两项平均综合成绩中，最终的入取率分别是28%（92届）和19.17% (90届)。<ref name=collegedata>{{cite web| title = Shimer College| publisher = CollegeData| url = https://www.collegedata.com/cs/data/college/college_pg01_tmpl.jhtml?schoolId=1356| accessdate = 2010-06-01| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110724204156/https://www.collegedata.com/cs/data/college/college_pg01_tmpl.jhtml?schoolId=1356| archive-date = 2011-07-24| dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>For ACT percentile: {{cite web | title = ACT High School Profile Report | publisher = ACT | url = http://www.act.org/news/data/07/pdf/National2007.pdf | accessdate = 2010-02-23 | page = 10 | format = PDF | archive-date = 2009-08-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090827003248/http://www.act.org/news/data/07/pdf/National2007.pdf | dead-url = no }}. For SAT percentile: {{cite web | title = SAT Percentile Ranks for Males, Females and Total Group | url = http://professionals.collegeboard.com/profdownload/sat_percentile_ranks_composite_cr_m_w.pdf | publisher = CollegeBoard | accessdate = 2010-05-12 | format = PDF | archive-date = 2009-11-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091122071642/http://professionals.collegeboard.com/profdownload/sat_percentile_ranks_composite_cr_m_w.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>

夏默的早期招生计划也接受在读的高中生入学，这项计划起于1950年。<ref name = "bigideas"/> 当时，该计划得到福特基金会、卡耐基基金会和其他基金会的支持。<ref name = completebook/> 进入学院的10年级和11年级高中生（16或17岁）会学习与其他学生同样的课程。学院会考虑给那些在某些方面有浓郁兴趣的学生实施激励机制，激发他们自主的学习态度，使他们将对知识的渴望作为一种最重要的能力来对待。<ref name = completebook/> 夏默也积极鼓励那些在家自学的学生报考，并特别他们提供适当的教育证明（如那些缺乏成绩单的在家自学者）。<ref>{{cite book | title = Homeschooling High School: Planning Ahead for College Admission | url = https://archive.org/details/homeschoolinghig0000denn_m6y1 | page = [https://archive.org/details/homeschoolinghig0000denn_m6y1/page/244 244] | last = Dennis | first = Jeanne Gowen | location = Lynwood, WA | publisher = Emerald Books | year = 2004 | isbn = 1932096116 }}</ref> 2008年，有16%的新生就是年少的高中生或同龄的在家自学者。<ref>{{cite news | title = Entering Class by the Numbers | newspaper = Symposium | date = Fall 2008 | page = 2 | url = http://alumni.shimer.edu/s/1028/images/editor_documents/Symposiums/08%20Fall%20Symposium.pdf | publisher = Shimer College | accessdate = 2010-04-28 | format = PDF | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100609191325/http://alumni.shimer.edu/s/1028/images/editor_documents/Symposiums/08%20Fall%20Symposium.pdf | archivedate = 2010-06-09 }}</ref>

2009年至2010年，学院全日制学生的学杂费是21000美元，食宿费是12000美元。有91%的本科生会得到学院的资助，每个学生平均的全部资助额为10594美元。<ref>{{cite book | pages = [https://archive.org/details/collegemoneyhand00pete/page/448 448]–449| title =  Peterson's College Money Handbook 2009| url = https://archive.org/details/collegemoneyhand00pete| location = Lawrenceville, NJ | publisher = Peterson's | edition = 26th | year = 2008 | isbn = 0768926254 }}</ref>

