2009年，由《华盛顿月刊》组织的院校排名中，夏默位列文科类第82名，<ref name="USUnivRankings_Wamo_LA">{{cite web |url=http://www.washingtonmonthly.com/college_guide/rankings/liberal_arts_rank.php |title=The Washington Monthly Liberal Arts Rankings |year=2009 |publisher=''The Washington Monthly'' |accessdate=2009-12-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091217103228/http://www.washingtonmonthly.com/college_guide/rankings/liberal_arts_rank.php |archivedate=2009-12-17 }}</ref> 而当时的《美国新闻和世界报道》未排定夏默的名次。<ref name="USUnivRankings_USNWR_LA">{{cite web |url=http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/college/liberal-arts-search |work=America's Best Colleges 2009 |title=Liberal Arts Colleges Rankings |publisher=U.S. News & World Report |year=2009 |accessdate=2009-05-18 |archive-date=2009-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090418201302/http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/college/liberal-arts-search/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>  2006年，在基于“稳健顶尖”、“传统自由”和“忠诚度”因素的全美50所院校的选拔赛中，夏默获选第一名。这次选拔的目的是要突出“课程应该采用一种特别的方式与美国人开拓创新的核心价值观和西方活跃的思想传统联系起来”。<ref>{{cite book | title = All-American Colleges: Top Schools for Conservatives, Old-Fashioned Liberals, and People of Faith | publisher = Intercollegiate Studies Institute | location = Wilmington, Delaware | year = 2006 | ISBN = 71849223}}</ref> 美国巴朗系列教育有限公司认定夏默是其三百所最优质的学院客户之一，并阐明“夏默课程的成功取决于对知识诠释的伟大理念和教师在教学上的协调技能，这些教师因能够将‘想象’变成“辉煌”而受到人们的称赞”。<ref name = barrons>{{cite book |title = Barron's Best Buys In College Education |url = https://archive.org/details/barronsbestbuysi0007solo | publisher = Barrons Educational Series | location = Hauppauge, New York | year = 2002 | edition = 7th | isbn = 0764120182 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/barronsbestbuysi0007solo/page/132 132]–134}}</ref> 2000年，《新闻透视》杂志认定夏默为一所全国最[[政治正确|政治正确]]的学院。一份被认可的列表显示：“一所具有影响力的传统课程的院校不会被多元化和差异化的时髦教育现象和盲目崇拜所困扰”。<ref>{{cite news | title = Shimer College Proud of Non-P.C. Rating | newspaper = Chicago Tribune | last = Hussain | first = Rummana | date = 2000-09-28 | url = http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2000-09-28/news/0009280390_1_illinois-school-board-educationally-sound | accessdate = 2010-04-24 | archive-date = 2014-12-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141217230921/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2000-09-28/news/0009280390_1_illinois-school-board-educationally-sound | dead-url = no }}</ref>

2007年，夏默加入了由非盈利组织—教育保护协会发起的全国性联合抵制大学排名调查活动。<ref>{{cite web | title = Presidents' Letter | url = http://www.educationconservancy.org/presidents_letter.html | publisher = The Education Conservancy | date = 2007-05-10 | accessdate = 2010-05-24 | archive-date = 2017-12-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171215091351/http://www.educationconservancy.org/presidents_letter.html | dead-url = no }}</ref> 第十任院长威廉·格雷格·赖斯说“夏默之所做得好，是我们时常告诫自己要与时俱进，不断与过去的最杰出的理性思想保持一致，不为美国新闻上的说三道四所折服”。<ref>{{cite web | title = Shimer College Joins Anti-Rankings Effort | publisher = Shimer College | url = http://www.shimer.edu/newsandevents/anti-ranking-effort.cfm | accessdate = 2010-04-24 | archive-date = 2010-05-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100527135420/http://www.shimer.edu/newsandevents/anti-ranking-effort.cfm | dead-url = yes }}</ref> 几乎所有的夏默学生都要参加GRE学考试，这是一项标准化的研究生入学考试，大四学生的考分会超过其他三个低年级的考生，根据91届的平均录取分值分析，他们“被认为在考试的口头表达与分析项目中，得分排在最优位置”。<ref name=magazinelauds>{{cite news | title = Magazine Lauds Shimer College | last = Sweeney | first = Annie | newspaper = Chicago Sun-Times | date = 2000-10-03 | url = http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-4565471.html | format = fee required | accessdate = 2010-04-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121104010145/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-4565471.html | archive-date = 2012-11-04 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref name = smallshimer>{{cite news | title = Small Shimer College Ranks High in Sending Students on to Ph.D.s | last = Flink | first = John | newspaper = Chicago Tribune | date = 1998-01-26 | url = http://proquest.umi.com/pqdweb?did=25606088&sid=1&Fmt=3&clientId=11417&RQT=309&VName=PQD | format = fee required | accessdate = 2010-04-23}}</ref>2009年《华盛顿月刊》的一份报告显示，夏默在美国文科类院校排名中，哲学博士研究生比率位列第三名。<ref>{{cite journal | title = Liberal Arts College Rankings | work = College Guide | journal = The Washington Monthly | url = http://www.washingtonmonthly.com/college_guide/rankings/liberal_arts_rank.php | accessdate = 2010-05-05 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20091217103228/http://www.washingtonmonthly.com/college_guide/rankings/liberal_arts_rank.php | archivedate = 2009-12-17 }}</ref>1998年威斯康星大学的一份研究认为，在文科类院校中，夏默博士生的比率是最高的；在全国本科生的排名中居第三名。<ref name = magazinelauds/> 据高等教育数据分享机构的研究显示，夏末位列全美大专院校哲学博士毕业率的第七位；而在语言类院校其哲学博士比率位居第一。<ref name="bourque">{{cite journal|url=http://www.jstor.org/pss/20027548|page=265|first=Susan C. | last = Bourque|journal=Daedalus|title=Reassessing Research: Liberal Arts Colleges and the Social Sciences|year=1999|volume=28|issue=1|accessdate=2010-04-27}}</ref><ref name="linguistics">{{cite web|url=http://www.insidecollege.com/reno/Where-Linguistics-PhDs-Received-Their-Undergraduate-Degrees/169/list.do|title=Where Linguistics PhDs Received their Undergraduate Degrees|work=Inside College|publisher=Inside College|accessdate=2010-04-25|archive-date=2010-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100701125208/http://www.insidecollege.com/reno/Where-Linguistics-PhDs-Received-Their-Undergraduate-Degrees/169/list.do|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 校园 ==

[[File:IIT_Galvin_Library.jpg|thumb]]

2006年，夏默重新将校园定位在伊利诺伊科技学院的校园内。在过去的25年中，夏默校址在伊利诺伊州的沃基根, 是由老旧房舍、旧女青年基督会和一幢公寓大楼组成的松散集合体。<ref name=celebratingshimer>{{cite news | title = Celebrating Shimer | newspaper = The Waukegan News-Sun | date = 2003-05-17 | last = Moran | first = Dan | url = http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1N1-0FEC012CB94C23E5.html | format = fee required | accessdate = 2010-05-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121104014126/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1N1-0FEC012CB94C23E5.html | archive-date = 2012-11-04 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = College Celebrates Move to Chicago | newspaper = Chicago Tribune | date = 2006-09-06 | url = http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/chicagotribune/access/1142816641.html?FMT=FT&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Oct+9%2C+2006&author=Chicago+Tribune&pub=Chicago+Tribune&desc=College+celebrates+move+to+Chicago | format = fee required | accessdate = 2010-04-22}}</ref> 第十任院长赖斯相信，新校址可以更广泛地吸引学生和捐赠者，还会扩大对学生的服务范围(如：餐厅和体育设施)，并有机会同科技学院进行学术合作。<ref>{{cite news | title = Shimer College OKs Move to IIT campus | newspaper = Chicago Tribune | date = 2006-01-20 | format = fee required |url = http://proquest.umi.com/pqdweb?did=972293981&sid=1&Fmt=3&clientId=11417&RQT=309&VName=PQD| accessdate = 2010-04-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Struggling College May Move; Shimer Considers Relocating To IIT | newspaper = Chicago Tribune | date = 2005-11-23| last = Bell | first = Barbara | url = http://proquest.umi.com/pqdweb?did=930302721&sid=1&Fmt=3&clientId=11417&RQT=309&VName=PQD | format = fee required | accessdate = 2010-04-22}}</ref>

120英亩（48.6公顷）的中心校园被第33街和伊利诺伊大街所围绕，距芝加哥环城路南部约3英里，历史上与芝加哥南面的布朗兹维勒（Bronzeville）相邻。.<ref>{{cite web | title = IIT History – Inventing the Future | publisher = Illinois Institute of Technology | url = http://www.iit.edu/about/history/inventing_the_future.shtml | accessdate = 2010-04-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100527110847/http://www.iit.edu/about/history/inventing_the_future.shtml | archive-date = 2010-05-27 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Visitor Information | url = http://www.iit.edu/about/visitor_information.shtml | publisher = Illinois Institute of Technology | accessdate = 2010-04-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100508013455/http://iit.edu/about/visitor_information.shtml | archive-date = 2010-05-08 | dead-url = yes }}</ref> 夏默校址曾以黑人都会区闻名，历史上这一地区有许多著名的非裔居民和机构，是芝加哥的一处地标，20世纪50年代曾兴旺一时。<ref name = NRexcerpt>{{cite web | title = Excerpt from the National Register Nomination for Chicago's Black Metropolis | publisher = National Park Service | url = http://www.nps.gov/nr/twhp/wwwlps/lessons/53black/53factsr.htm | accessdate = 2010-04-22 | archive-date = 2010-11-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101130002815/http://www.nps.gov/nr/twhp/wwwlps/lessons/53black/53factsr.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>那一时期留存下来的一些建筑物于1986年被联合编入[[国家史迹名录|国家史迹名录]]，1998年被评定为芝加哥地标。<ref>{{citation |url = http://pdfhost.focus.nps.gov/docs/NRHP/Text/64000173.pdf |title = National Register of Historic Places Inventory/Nomination: Black Metropolis Thematic Nomination |date = 1985-11-07 |publisher = National Park Service |accessdate = 2010-04-22 |format = PDF |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121008180819/http://pdfhost.focus.nps.gov/docs/NRHP/Text/64000173.pdf |archive-date = 2012-10-08 |dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = City Council Approves "Black Renaissance" Literary Landmarks | publisher = City of Chicago | url = http://www.cityofchicago.org/city/en/depts/dcd/provdrs/hist/news/2010/feb/committee_approvesblackrenaissanceliterarylandmarks.html | accessdate = 2011-05-10 | archive-date = 2011-09-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110925190734/http://www.cityofchicago.org/city/en/depts/dcd/provdrs/hist/news/2010/feb/committee_approvesblackrenaissanceliterarylandmarks.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>

夏默现在的校园由现代派建筑师卢德维格-密斯-凡德罗主持设计，该建筑被《纽约时报》评为20世纪伟大的建筑艺术造型之一。<ref name = miesdies>{{cite news | title = Mies van der Rohe Dies at 83; Leader of Modern Architecture | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 1969-08-19 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/learning/general/onthisday/bday/0327.html | accessdate = 2010-04-22 | archive-date = 2010-08-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100805061404/http://www.nytimes.com/learning/general/onthisday/bday/0327.html | dead-url = no }}</ref> 凡德罗曾为伊利诺伊科技学院校园构想主要设计计划，结果有20项设计作品被院方采纳，这是他最具雄心壮志的设计工程之一，也是他在世界建筑业界设计成果的最伟大展现。<ref>{{cite web  | title = Mies at IIT  | publisher = Illinois Institute of Technology  | url = http://guides.library.iit.edu/content.php?pid=50213&sid=368875  | accessdate = 2011-05-10  | archive-date = 2011-07-20  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110720003517/http://guides.library.iit.edu/content.php?pid=50213&sid=368875  | dead-url = no  }}</ref> 校园的园景工程由凡罗德的同行密友欧非雷德-科尔德维尔主持设计（Alfred Caldwell）,该工程是普列里景观建筑师学院的最后一件代表作。<ref>{{cite journal | title = The Last Master | last = Domer | first = Dennis | journal = Inland Architect Magazine | url = http://www.inlandarchitectmag.com/pdf/caldwell.pdf | page = 69 | accessdate = 2010-04-22 | format = PDF | archive-date = 2011-07-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110713034910/http://www.inlandarchitectmag.com/pdf/caldwell.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Alfred Caldwell | url = http://www.iit.edu/about/history/hall_of_fame/alfred_caldwell.shtml | publisher = Illinois Institute of Technology | accessdate = 2010-04-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140518061137/http://www.iit.edu/about/history/hall_of_fame/alfred_caldwell.shtml | archive-date = 2014-05-18 | dead-url = yes }}</ref> 1976年,美国建筑师学会将这个景观评定为全国200处最重要的景观建筑艺术之一。<ref>{{cite book | title = The Politics Of Place: A History of Zoning in Chicago | page = 51 | last1 = Schweiterman | last2 = Caspall | last3 = Heron | first1 = Joseph P | first2 = Dana M | first3 = Jane | location = Chicago, IL | publisher = Lake Claremont Press | year = 2006 | isbn = 1893121267}}</ref> 2005年，科技学院的主校园被登录《国家史迹名录》。<ref>{{citation |url = http://pdfhost.focus.nps.gov/docs/NRHP/Text/05000871.pdf |title = National Register of Historic Places Inventory/Nomination: Illinois Institute of Technology Academic Campus |date = 2005-08-12 |publisher = National Park Service |accessdate = 2010-04-22 |format = PDF |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121008180841/http://pdfhost.focus.nps.gov/docs/NRHP/Text/05000871.pdf |archive-date = 2012-10-08 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>

[[File:McCormick_Tribune_060304.jpg|thumb]] 夏默占地17000平凡英尺（1580平方米），这里之前是天然气科技协会大楼联合体的第一层和第二层，曾长期租个伊利诺伊科技学院使用。<ref name=citylights>{{cite web | title = Great Books and City Lights | publisher = Inside Higher Ed | last = Epstein | first = David | url = http://m.insidehighered.com/news/2006/01/23/shimer | date = 2006-01-23 | accessdate = 2010-04-23 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110514065132/http://m.insidehighered.com/news/2006/01/23/shimer | archivedate = 2011-05-14 }}</ref>这幢由凡德罗的设计的连体大楼建于1947年和1955年之间，共有四栋建筑组成，南面的建筑临近美国的第一个工业核反应堆。<ref name = iitbuildings/>

选择寄宿的学生住在冈萨雷斯大楼，该大楼于2008年被完全改造为纯公寓式住宅。<ref>{{cite web | title = Housing Choices for Current Gunsaulus Hall Residents | publisher = Illinois Institute of Technology | url = http://www.iit.edu/housing/choices/gunsaulus_choices.shtml | accessdate = 2010-04-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100527212625/http://www.iit.edu/housing/choices/gunsaulus_choices.shtml | archive-date = 2010-05-27 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.iit.edu/housing/choices/gunsaulus_hall.shtml | title = Gunsaulus Hall | publisher = Illinois Institute of Technology | accessdate = 2010-04-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100516061730/http://iit.edu/housing/choices/gunsaulus_hall.shtml | archive-date = 2010-05-16 | dead-url = yes }}</ref> 夏默有通往保尔-V-格尔文图书馆的入口，该图书馆是伊利诺伊科技学院的主要研究型图书馆，藏书180万册，25500种期刊和广泛的电子文档资源。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://library.iit.edu/reports/LIBRARY_AR2007_final.pdf | title = IIT Libraries 2007 | publisher = Illinois Institute of Technology | accessdate = 2010-04-22 | format = PDF | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100525092928/http://library.iit.edu/reports/LIBRARY_AR2007_final.pdf | archivedate = 2010-05-25 }}</ref> 夏默在从沃基根迁来时，也将自己的1.5万册图书存于这个图书馆。<ref>{{cite news | title = Mega Book Sale; Shimer Moves Library  to Chicago Campus, Selling 10,000 Books; Get-Out-Of-Town Sale | newspaper = The Waukegan News Sun | last = Pagelow | first = Ryan | date = 2007-01-11 | accessdate = 2010-04-22 | url = http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1N1-1183891141773A98.html | format = fee required | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121104004459/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1N1-1183891141773A98.html | archive-date = 2012-11-04 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

科技学院对夏默学生开放的其他设施包括“麦考密克·丘比犹校园中心”(MTCC), 该中心由享有国际声誉的建筑师雷姆-库哈斯（Rem Koolhaas）于2003年设计建造。<ref name=koolhaas>{{cite news | title = IIT Architect Would Love Encore; Designer Of Student Center Would Like To Build High-Rise Here | newspaper = Chicago Sun-Times | last = Reed | first = Cheryl | date = 2003-10-01 | url = http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-1509786.html | format = fee required | accessdate = 2010-04-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121104004444/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-1509786.html | archive-date = 2012-11-04 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref name = architecturematters>{{cite book | page = 178 | title = Why Architecture Matters: Lessons from Chicago | last= Kamin | first = Blair | location = Chicago | publisher = University of Chicago Press | year = 2002 | isbn = 0226423212 }}</ref>
该里是学生的主要活动中心，设有快食店、新闻站、休息区、会议中心、计算机工作站、书店和大礼堂。<ref name = architecturematters/> 夏默学生还可使用科技学院的主要体育场所、临近大学体育队的凯亭体育中心，该中心向学生提供拍球戏、保龄球、攀岩、各式舞蹈运动以及班级间的篮球、排球、足球对抗赛。<ref>{{cite web | title = Intramurals and Recreation | publisher = Illinois Institute of Technology | url = http://www.illinoistechathletics.com/f/Intramurals_and_Recreation.php | accessdate = 2011-05-10 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110414010355/http://www.illinoistechathletics.com/f/Intramurals_and_Recreation.php | archivedate = 2011-04-14 }}</ref>

== 学院管理 ==

[[File:Shimer_assembly_applause.jpg|thumb]]

夏默是一家非盈利性的法人机构，设有一个独立且永续存在的“受托人委员会”，由她管理学院事务和财产。委员会授权给学院最高执行官-院长、教务长以及与学术事务相关的教师，由他们管理学院事务。{{sfn|Shimer College Catalog|2009|p=31}}截至2009年，这个委员会共有36名成员（包括3名学生和2名教师），最终会发展到40名，总负责人是圣约翰大学校长克里斯多夫-B-纳尔森（Christopher B. Nelson）。<ref name = menace>{{cite news | title = The Conservative Menace | newspaper = Chicago Reader | last = Isaacs | first = Deanna | date = 2009-12-10 | url = http://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/the-conservative-menace/Content?oid=1251260 | accessdate = 2010-04-23 | archive-date = 2010-05-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100501171724/http://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/the-conservative-menace/Content?oid=1251260 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

“推进全民化管理是受托委员的一个使命”，夏默说，“在世界高等教育机构中，能在更广的围内致力于内部自治是很稀罕的事”。{{sfn|Shimer College Catalog|2009|p=30}} 1977年以来，夏默已经开始由一个叫做评审议会的团体在学院实施内部自治，由尽可能多的公众选出的学生和教师担任所有的行政机构成员，包括受托委员会成员，这样，传统学院和大学自上而下的官僚主义作风，在夏默会被尽职尽责的民主对话所取代。{{sfn|Kavaloski|1979| p=243}} “评审议会”没有法律上的授权，但却在管理学院的重大事情，夏默说，“这就是基于‘公共评审’而形成的一种管理制度，使执行者具有忠诚的职业操守”。{{sfn|Constitution of the Assembly|2008|p=2}} 就在夏默非正式迁入沃基根校址前的几年里，“评审议会”于1980年就依章程正式运作。<ref name="particulars">{{cite journal|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20010307132235/http://www.shimer.edu/particulars.html |archivedate=2001-03-07 |title=On Not Knowing the Particulars: The Mission of the Assembly |journal=Promulgates |volume=7 |issue=1 |last1=Shiner |last2=Wikse |first1=David |first2=Jack |url=http://www.shimer.edu/particulars.html |accessdate=2010-04-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>“议会”的投票成员包括学生、教师、行政人员、职员和受托人。<ref>{{cite news | title = Big Trouble at Little Shimer: What’s Happening to Chicago’s Great Books College? | last = Feldman | first = Sam | date = 2010-04-03 | url = http://chicagoweekly.net/2010/03/03/big-trouble-at-little-shimer-whats-happening-to-chicagos-great-books-college/ | accessdate = 2010-07-07 | newspaper = Chicago Weekly | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100924112109/http://chicagoweekly.net/2010/03/03/big-trouble-at-little-shimer-whats-happening-to-chicagos-great-books-college/ | archivedate = 2010-09-24 }}</ref> 校友也是“议会”的成员，但不投票。“议会”向学院的管理部门提供建议，并通过其在议会委员会的权限指导学院的商业、学术、计划、预算、招生、投诉、金融援助、和学生生活等事务。“议会”的全部成员由教师、职员和议会选出的学生组成。{{sfn|Constitution of the Assembly|2008|pp=9–11}}

夏默学生也会派出代表自由参与科技学院的“学生自治协会”(SGA)，,充当校方与表达学生观点之校园论坛的联络员。<ref>{{cite web | title = Bylaws of the Student Government Association of Illinois Institute of Technology | date = 2009-09-22 | url = http://sga.studgov.com/assets/SGA_Bylaws1.doc | pages = 11–12 | publisher = Student Government Association of Illinois Institute of Technology | accessdate = 2010-04-27 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110827023801/http://sga.studgov.com/assets/SGA_Bylaws1.doc | archivedate = 2011-08-27 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = About | url = http://sga.studgov.com/about | publisher = Student Government Association of Illinois Institute of Technology | accessdate = 2011-05-10 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110716155508/http://sga.studgov.com/about | archivedate = 2011-07-16 }}</ref>
==学生生活==

[[File:2010_Shimer_Commencement_Raya_reads.jpg|2010年夏默学院毕业典礼上，正在作毕业告别演说的学生拉娅·卡尔（Raya Carr ）。]]
《纽约时报》称夏默为“美国最袖珍的文科院校之一”，并将这里的学生描述为“... 只知道在毕业时发表告别演讲，是不入流的大学生。他们所钟爱的只有书本，而对传统的教育风格不屑一顾。许多人认为这些学生并没有良好的大学经历”。<ref name = smallcampus>{{cite news | title = Small Campus, Big Books | last = Johnson | first = Dirk | date = 2007-11-04 | newspaper = The New York Times | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2007/11/04/education/edlife/shimer.html | accessdate = 2010-05-22 | archive-date = 2012-03-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120319110621/http://www.nytimes.com/2007/11/04/education/edlife/shimer.html | dead-url = no }}</ref> 夏默学生倾向于个人主义，热衷成为思想家，这激发了人们的质疑与好奇。<ref>{{cite book | title = Peterson's Four-Year Colleges 2007 | url = https://archive.org/details/undergraduategui00pete_0 | publisher = Thompson Peterson's | location = Lawrenceville, New Jersey |  year = 2006| page = [https://archive.org/details/undergraduategui00pete_0/page/2248 2248]| isbn =0768921538  }}</ref>2009年，夏默招收了100名学生，他们来自国内22个州，而且多数来自伊利诺伊州；另有2名来自外国的学生。<ref name = petersonsmidwest>{{cite book | title = Peterson's Colleges in the Midwest | publisher = Peterson's | location = Lawrenceville, New Jersey |  year = 2009 | page = 61 | isbn = 0768926904}}</ref>学院80%的学生为白人，40%的学生年龄为25岁。首年入读的全日制学生，有70% 会进入第二学年继续就读；55%会在6年内毕业。

排外性的[[兄弟会与姊妹会|兄弟会与姊妹会]]以及其他组织在夏默是不被允许的，学院没有组织自己的俱乐部或体育项目。<ref>{{cite web | title = Student Life | url = http://www.shimer.edu/aboutshimercollege/studentlife.cfm | publisher = Shimer College | accessdate = 2010-04-21 | archive-date = 2010-05-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100512165419/http://www.shimer.edu/aboutshimercollege/studentlife.cfm | dead-url = yes }}</ref> 夏默有邀请所人共餐的传统，这种传统课可以追溯到早期的沃基根校园，这一天，大家会聚集在一起享用家常便饭，同时谈论感兴趣的话题，并最终促成了评审议会的诞生。<ref name = "particulars"/>欧伦杰马术节是夏默两年一度的才能展示会，这项活动可以追溯到1960年代的学院传统活动。这一天，学院会邀请学生、教师、校友进行个人或集体的诗朗诵、唱歌、弹奏乐曲或讲笑话。<ref>{{cite web | title = Orange Horse | date = 2008-11-15 | url = http://www.shimer.edu/newsandevents/upload/Orange-Horse.pdf | publisher = Shimer College | accessdate = 2010-04-27 | format = PDF | archive-date = 2010-05-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100527134812/http://www.shimer.edu/newsandevents/upload/Orange-Horse.pdf | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

1967年，在人文系教授艾琳·布坎南（Eileen Buchanan）的指导下，夏默为学生开设了戏曲课程。布坎南也是一名职业演员和导演， 他以自己的导演创作补充了夏默课程的不足，为那些想参与戏曲事业的学生提供了机会。<ref>{{cite web | title = Eileen Powers Buchanan, Professor of Humanities | url = http://www.shimer.edu/aboutshimercollege/EilleneBuchanan.cfm | publisher = Shimer College | accessdate = 2010-04-21 | archive-date = 2009-10-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091016071413/http://www.shimer.edu/aboutshimercollege/EilleneBuchanan.cfm | dead-url = yes }}</ref> 夏默学生在芝加哥本地上演的作品有安东·契诃夫（Anton Chekhov）的《凡亚叔叔》和伊芙-恩斯勒（Eve Ensler）的《佛吉亚独白》<ref>
{{cite web | title =Spring Theater – Uncle Vanya | publisher =Shimer College | url =http://alumni.shimer.edu/s/1028/index.aspx?sid=1028&gid=1&pgid=252&cid=1191&ecid=1191&crid=0&calpgid=61&calcid=1011 | accessdate =2010-04-27 | deadurl =yes | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20100513071607/http://alumni.shimer.edu/s/1028/index.aspx?sid=1028&gid=1&pgid=252&cid=1191&ecid=1191&crid=0&calpgid=61&calcid=1011 | archivedate =2010-05-13 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Shimer College Theater to Present "The Vagina Monologues" | work = IIT Today | publisher = Illinois Institute of Technology | url = http://www.iit.edu/publications/iittoday/archive.php?id=1284&page=140&totalrows=7547 | date = 2006-10-17 | accessdate = 2010-04-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110622020858/http://www.iit.edu/publications/iittoday/archive.php?id=1284&page=140&totalrows=7547 | archive-date = 2011-06-22 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

